esources.html&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1585229707297000&amp;usg=AFQjCNE8OXYhOCxkTRAkWu2-U9AVWdlRng"> - Resources to help mentors talk to children about Covid-19</a></li>        <li><a href="https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/community/colleges-universities/considerations.html" target="_blank">Guidance for Institutions of Higher Education</a></li>      </ul>      <p>&nbsp;</p>          </div>    <button class="accordion"> Working with Communities and Systems</button>    <div class="panel">      <p><img src="../images/colorful-wheel-cogs-in-a-row.jpg" width="1000" height="366" alt="colorful cog wheels in a row" /></p>      <p>This is a time where coming together (especially within communities and systems) is necessary to gain strength and momentum as we battle the COVID-19 health crisis.</p>      <ul>        <li><a href="https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/php/public-health-communicators-get-your-community-ready.html" target="_blank" data-saferedirecturl="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/php/public-health-communicators-get-your-community-ready.html&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1585229707297000&amp;usg=AFQjCNGTvi1awl6nBACTAz8EAUM_Fj7jHw">Interim Guidance: Public Health Communicators Get Your Community Ready for Coronavirus Disease 2019 (COVID-19)</a></li>        <li><a href="https://indivisible.org/resource/community-building-during-covid">Community Building During the Coronavirus</a></li>        <li><a href="https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/community/organizations/index.html" target="_blank" data-saferedirecturl="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/community/organizations/index.html&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1585229707297000&amp;usg=AFQjCNHyV9LjZb9pQShiv9kPaRekvNU-kg">Interim Guidance for Community and Faith Leaders (CDC)</a></li>        <li><a href="https://wamu.org/story/20/03/17/6-ways-you-can-help-your-community-fight-the-impacts-of-coronavirus/" target="_blank"